Welcome to WikiTok. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we handle any information when you use our application.
Information We Collect
Our app collects the following types of information:
Usage Data:
Anonymous statistics about how you interact with the app, including articles viewed and time spent on each article.
Device Information:
Basic information about your device type, operating system version, and app version for troubleshooting and improvements.
Cached Content:
We temporarily store Wikipedia articles locally on your device to improve performance and enable offline access.
How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for:
Improving and optimizing the app performance
Understanding how users interact with different features
Troubleshooting technical issues
Providing relevant content recommendations
Data Storage and Security
All locally stored data is encrypted and securely maintained on your device. We do not transfer any personal information to external servers except for anonymous usage statistics.
Third-Party Services
Our app integrates with the following third-party services:
Wikipedia API:
Used to fetch article content. When you access articles, your requests are subject to Wikipedia's privacy policy.
Google Play Services:
Used for app analytics and crash reporting. This service collects anonymous usage data in accordance with Google's privacy policy.
Your Rights
You have the right to:
Clear your local cache and stored articles
Opt-out of anonymous usage statistics collection
Request information about what data we collect
Request deletion of your usage data
Children's Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.
Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy in the app and updating the "Last Updated" date.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our practices, please contact us at:
contact@wikitok.app